# Changelog maintenance

## Before implementing

Read `CHANGELOG.md` **Unreleased** and latest version section. Check **Not yet built** before assuming a feature exists.

## Update when (same session)

- Backlog story completes (moves to Done in `SPRINT.md`)
- User-facing or structural capability ships
- Sprint closes — promote `[Unreleased]` to versioned section

## Do NOT log when

- Docs-only grooming without new capability
- Refactors with no new capability
- Partial/WIP — wait until acceptance criteria pass

## How to write

Under `## [Unreleased]` → `### Added`:

- Capability-first; include story ID `(W-01-S03)`
- Name key artifacts when helpful
- Update `### Not yet built` — remove shipped items

## Sprint close

1. Rename `[Unreleased]` to `## X.Y.Z — YYYY-MM-DD — Sprint N — Title`
2. Add **Stories:** line
3. Fresh `[Unreleased]` section
4. `0.1.0` = Spike; bump minor for M1/M2 milestones per `IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md`

Do not ask permission — update on completed stories unless user said not to.
